<title>Description</title>


<para>A <tag>SystemItem</tag> identifies any system-related item or term.
The <tag class='attribute'>Class</tag> attribute defines a
number of common system-related terms.
</para>

<para>Many inline elements in DocBook are, in fact, system-related.  Some of
the objects identified by the <tag class='attribute'>Class</tag>
